articles.author: Lauren Goode, Paresh Dave, Will Knight
articles.title: What Donald Trump's Win Will Mean for Big Tech - WIRED
articles.description: Donald Trump's approach to Big Tech has oscillated between calls for stricter regulations for some players and a hands-off approach for others. Here's how he might steer tech policy in a second term.
